The proof uses `Measure.map_eq_comap_of_inverse` to handle the graph complement (which is an involution), and `bernoulliOn_map_compl` to relate the Bernoulli distributions. We also use the injectivity of `edgeSet` to relate operations on graphs to operations on edge sets.

